00:02:55.173 --> 00:02:56.646
of that happening...

00:02:56.646 --> 00:03:01.646
So 18 and a half, it's a hand drawn chart,

00:03:04.793 --> 00:03:07.585
or histogram, so you have to bear with me.

00:03:07.585 --> 00:03:12.585
So it's roughly there, and then four

00:03:14.928 --> 00:03:19.928
was 32.4 percent, so that is up here.

00:03:20.907 --> 00:03:25.907
