00:03:36.846 --> 00:03:41.793
30.3 percent, slightly
lower, just like that.

00:03:41.793 --> 00:03:46.251
And it will look like this.

00:03:46.251 --> 00:03:51.251
30.3 percent, and finally,
six is 11.8 percent.

00:03:52.635 --> 00:03:53.726
So really, this whole video was just

00:03:53.726 --> 00:03:56.768
